---
import Title from '../components/Title.astro';
import PrimaryLayout from '../layouts/PrimaryLayout.astro';
---

<PrimaryLayout>
  <Title />

  <div
    id='info-card'
    class='flex flex-row items-start justify-start w-screen pl-28 place-items-baseline'
  >
    <div class='max-w-xl'>
      <h2 class='mt-0 text-4xl font-bold'>Woah</h2>
      <p>
        Who are we? What are we? In a nutshell, currently it's just me (Artie)
        who's in the group and I wannna somewhat expand this group to include my
        other friends, I don't care if they know how to code I'll teach them, I
        just want to get more members and collaborate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    id='info-card'
    class='flex flex-row items-start justify-end w-screen mt-5 pr-28 place-items-baseline'
  >
    <div class='max-w-xl'>
      <h2 class='mt-0 text-4xl font-bold'>Members</h2>
      <p>
        Hey, I'm Artie! The only Member and Lead-Developer in this organization,
        I'm only accepting friends so please, don't attempt to join if I don't
        know you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PrimaryLayout>
